org.encog.bot.rss
Class RSS

java.lang.Object
  org.encog.bot.rss.RSS

public class RSS
extends Object

This is the class that actually parses the RSS and builds a collection of RSSItems. To make use of this class call the load method with a URL that points to RSS.
